.TH "pdc_lan_station_id" 9 "pdc_lan_station_id" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
pdc_lan_station_id \- Get the LAN address.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" pdc_lan_station_id
.BI "(char *lan_addr "  ","
.BI "unsigned long hpa "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "lan_addr" 12
The return buffer.
.IP "hpa" 12
The network device HPA.
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Get the LAN station address when it is not directly available from the LAN hardware.
